data.description: OPPORTUNITY investors & sweat equity Buyer! Priced to Sell! Tons of potential in this fixer with 4 bedrooms & 1.5 bathrooms. Main level features 3 bedrooms, 1 full bath, kitchen, spacious living room that opens to formal dining room w/slider door to the covered patio and generous yard. Desirable hardwood floors under the carpets on the main level. Full basement has access from the interior of the home & the garage, is partially finished with a non-conforming 4th bedroom, large bonus/family area, half bath & laundry room area. This home sits on a versatile corner lot with access to the 3 car oversized garage from both corner streets. Amenities incl good floor plan, newer gas furnace, huge RV parking area, lots of storage areas & convenient location close to schools, parks, shopping & freeway access.
